[{"id":"c3cb4183755547f4fe87bc6cc27f2a9c","from":"Peter Mandelson","from_email":"petermandelson@btinternet.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"RE:","date":"2008-06-25T10:55:32.000Z","formatted_date":"Jun 25, 2008","formatted_time":"10:55 AM","body":"I think the world of you and I feel hopeless and furious about what has\nhappened. I can still barely understand it. It just could not happen in\nBritain. You have to be incredibly resilient, fight for early release and be\nphilosophical about it as much as you can. Reinaldo insists that everything\ncan be turned into an opportunity and that you will come through it and be\nstronger for it. The whole thing has been years of torture and now you have\nto show the world how big a person you are, and how strong. Your friends\nstay with you and love you.\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nThe Rt. Hon.Peter Mandelson\n\nEuropean Commissioner for Trade\n\n \n\nTel: 00322 295 6881\n\n-----Original Message-----\nFrom: J. Epstein [mailto:jeeproject@yahoo.com] \nSent: 24 June 2008 19:59\nTo: Peter Mandelson\nSubject: Re:\n\n \n\n340 775 8111\n\n----- Original Message ----\nFrom: Peter Mandelson <petermandelson@btinternet.com>\nTo: J. Epstein <jeeproject@yahoo.com>\nSent: Tuesday, June 24, 2008 12:01:00 PM\nSubject: RE:\n\nI am phoning after conference call in half hour\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nThe Rt. Hon.Peter Mandelson\n\nEuropean Commissioner for Trade\n\n \n\nTel: 00322 295 6881\n\n-----Original Message-----\nFrom: J. Epstein [mailto:jeeproject@yahoo.com] \nSent: 24 June 2008 17:00\nTo: Peter Mandelson\nSubject: Re:\n\n \n\nbad news 18 months starting monday\n\n----- Original Message ----\nFrom: Peter Mandelson <petermandelson@btinternet.com>\nTo: J. Epstein <jeeproject@yahoo.com>\nSent: Wednesday, June 18, 2008 2:10:59 AM\nSubject: \n\nWhat your plans ? En route to Moscow..\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nThe Rt. Hon.Peter Mandelson\n\nEuropean 