years of torture and now you have to\nshow the world how big a person you are, and how strong. Your friends stay with\nyou and love you.</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><font size=2 color=navy face=Arial><span style='font-size:\n10.0pt;font-family:Arial;color:navy'>&nbsp;</span></font></p>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><font size=3 color=navy face=\"Times New Roman\"><span\nstyle='font-size:12.0pt;color:navy'>&nbsp;</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><font size=3 color=navy face=\"Times New Roman\"><span\nstyle='font-size:12.0pt;color:navy'>&nbsp;</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><font size=3 color=navy face=\"Times New Roman\"><span\nstyle='font-size:12.0pt;color:navy'>&nbsp;</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><font size=3 color=navy face=\"Times New Roman\"><span\nstyle='font-size:12.0pt;color:navy'>&nbsp;</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><font size=3 color=navy face=\"Times New Roman\"><span\nstyle='font-size:12.0pt;color:navy'>&nbsp;</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><strong><b><i><font size=2 color=navy face=Arial><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial;color:navy;font-style:italic'>The Rt.\nHon.</span></font></i></b></strong><strong><b><i><font size=2 color=navy\n face=Arial><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial;color:navy;\n font-style:italic'>Peter Mandelson</span></font></i></b></strong></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><em><i><font size=2 color=navy face=Arial><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial;color:navy'>European Commissioner for\nTrade</span></font></i></em></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><font size=3 color=navy face=\"Times New Roman\"><span\nstyle='font-size:12.0pt;color:navy'>&nbsp;</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><em><i><font size=2 color=navy face=Arial><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial;color:navy'>Tel: 00322 295 6881</span></font></i></em></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:36.0pt'><font size=2 face=Tahoma><span\nlang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0p